---
// CFP Section
---

<section class="section section--deep" id="cfp" aria-labelledby="cfp-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header">
      <span class="label label--light">04 — CFP</span>
      <hr class="rule-forest" />
      <h2 class="label label--light" id="cfp-heading">Call for papers</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-12 reveal">
      <div style="grid-column: 1 / 7;">
        <h2
          class="heading-1 text-white"
          style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);"
        >
          We want<br />
          <em
            class="text-mint"
            style="font-family:var(--serif); font-style:italic;"
            >practitioners.</em
          >
        </h2>
        <p
          style="font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height:1.75; max-width:44ch;"
        >
          People who have done the work, hit the walls, found the solutions, and
          can share those lessons in a concrete, actionable way. You do not need
          to be famous. You need to have something real to say.
        </p>

        <div class="cfp__timeline">
          <div class="cfp__row">
            <span>CFP opens</span>
            <span class="cfp__date">July 1, 2026</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cfp__row">
            <span>CFP closes</span>
            <span class="cfp__date">August 15, 2026</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cfp__row">
            <span>Notifications</span>
            <span class="cfp__date">September 15, 2026</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cfp__row">
            <span>Submit via</span>
            <span class="cfp__date">Sessionize</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="grid-column: 8 / 13;">
        <div class="cfp__card">
          <div
            class="label label--light"
            style="margin-bottom:var(--space-xs);"
          >
            We especially want
          </div>
          <ul class="cfp__list">
            <li>First-time speakers — we actively support you</li>
            <li>Africa-based engineers with local infra stories</li>
            <li>Engineers at African fintechs, telcos, startups</li>
            <li>Diaspora engineers with global-scale experience</li>
            <li>Open-source contributors and maintainers</li>
          </ul>

          <div
            style="height:1px; background:var(--mid); margin:var(--space-sm) 0;"
          >
          </div>

          <div
            class="label"
            style="margin-bottom:var(--space-xs); color:rgba(255,100,100,0.6);"
          >
            We will decline
          </div>
          <ul class="cfp__list cfp__list--decline">
            <li>Vendor sales pitches disguised as talks</li>
            <li>Talks with no concrete takeaways</li>
            <li>General intro content without depth</li>
          </ul>

          <a
            href="https://sessionize.com/infraconf-africa-2026/"
            class="btn btn--primary"
            style="margin-top:var(--space-md); width:100%; justify-content:center;"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >
            Submit your talk
            <svg
              width="14"
              height="14"
              viewBox="0 0 14 14"
              fill="none"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                d="M2 7h10M7 2l5 5-5 5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cfp__timeline {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--mid);
    border: 1px solid var(--mid);
  }

  .cfp__row {
    background: var(--deep);
    padding: 14px 18px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .cfp__date {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--mint);
  }

  .cfp__card {
    border: 1px solid var(--mid);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    height: 100%;
  }

  .cfp__list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .cfp__list li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 16px 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .cfp__list li::before {
    content: "—";
    font-family: var(--mono);
    color: var(--mint);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .cfp__list--decline li {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }
  .cfp__list--decline li::before {
    content: "×";
    color: rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid-12 > div:first-child {
      grid-column: 1 / -1 !important;
    }
    .grid-12 > div:last-child {
      grid-column: 1 / -1 !important;
    }
  }
</style>
